        "release": "v2.0.0",
        "priority": "low",
        "status": "planned",
        "rationale": "Not reserved words; huge surface. Beginner African packs should not need to translate type names or stdlib for control-flow-only transpilation.",
        "scopeNote": "Add only when Kola transpiles translated API calls at scale. PRINT (print / console.log / fmt.Println) is the existing pattern.",
        "designFirst": [
          "New tier or group in logical-tokens.json (e.g. stdlib, not core)",
          "Separate coverage rules — not part of official keyword gap checks",
          "Resolve naming collisions (e.g. Go MAP keyword vs map builtin)"
        ],
